text: Jindriska Holubkova is a female former international table tennis player from Czechoslovakia. ==Table tennis career== She won a gold medal in the women's team event at the 1938 World Table Tennis Championships. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:Czech female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Jindriska Holubkova
